Description: A computationally efficient solution for generating optimal experimental designs in Accelerated Life Testing (ALT) with multiple factors. Leveraging a Particle Swarm Optimization (PSO)-based hybrid algorithm, the package identifies optimal test plans that minimize estimation variance under specified failure models and stress profiles.
